tps://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/end-point-based-threshold-for-the-ambulatory-arterial-stiffness-index</guid></item><item><title>珍珠和牡蛎：使用基于敏感性的成像治疗高度活跃的迟发性多发性硬化症</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pearls-oy-sters-using-susceptibility-based-imaging-in-highly-active-late-onset-multiple-sclerosis</link><description>中央静脉征和顺磁性边缘病变可以帮助迟发性多发性硬化症的早期诊断，并且可以避免活检的需要。阅读这篇珍珠和牡蛎文章了解更多信息。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pearls-oy-sters-using-susceptibility-based-imaging-in-highly-active-late-onset-multiple-sclerosis2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 11:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/pearls-oy-sters-using-susceptibility-based-imaging-in-highly-active-late-onset-multiple-sclerosis</guid></item><item><title>定义神经结节病的复发和疾病活动系统回顾和拟议框架</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/defining-relapse-and-disease-activity-in-neurosarcoidosisa-systematic-review-and-proposed-framework</link><description>定义神经结节病的复发和疾病活动：系统评价和提出的框架。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/defining-relapse-and-disease-activity-in-neurosarcoidosisa-systematic-review-and-proposed-framework2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 11:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/defining-relapse-and-disease-activity-in-neurosarcoidosisa-systematic-review-and-proposed-framework</guid></item><item><title>使用人工智能改善心脏成像护理标准</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/using-ai-to-improve-standard-of-care-cardiac-imaging</link><description>心脏病是全球成人死亡的主要原因，使心血管疾病的诊断和管理成为全球健康的优先事项。超声心动图或心脏超声是医生用来诊断各种心脏病和病症的最常用成像工具之一。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/using-ai-to-improve-standard-of-care-cardiac-imaging2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 11:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/using-ai-to-improve-standard-of-care-cardiac-imaging</guid></item><item><title>锌如何保护受伤的动脉免于加速老化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-zinc-protects-injured-arteries-from-accelerated-aging</link><description>研究人员发表在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-zinc-protects-injured-arteries-from-accelerated-aging.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 11:14:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/how-zinc-protects-injured-arteries-from-accelerated-aging</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克：模拟之外还有什么？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/elon-musk-whats-outside-the-simulation</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 10:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/elon-musk-whats-outside-the-simulation</guid></item><item><title>婴儿心脏手术也能修复大脑网络</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/infant-heart-surgery-mends-brain-networks-too</link><description>出生时患有先天性心脏病 (CHD) 的婴儿通常会出现神经发育障碍，这些障碍会影响他们日后的生活，包括他们调节情绪和运动的能力。由于先天性心脏病是美国最常见的先天性疾病，研究人员渴望找到新的治疗方法。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/infant-heart-surgery-mends-brain-networks-too.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 10:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/infant-heart-surgery-mends-brain-networks-too</guid></item><item><title>之前和之后可以叠加吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-before-and-after-be-superposed</link><description>通过量子开关实验，研究人员试图揭示“不确定的因果顺序”——一种涉及事件前后叠加的量子现象。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-before-and-after-be-superposed2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 10:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-before-and-after-be-superposed</guid></item></channel></rss>